<div class="ui main text container">
<div class="ui segment">
  <%= image_tag("rubot_profile_pic.png", :class => "ui floated left image tiny ") %>

<h1 class="ui header">Welcome to <%= "#{Rails.application.config.client_name}" %>'s control panel!</h1>


<h3 class="ui header"><%= "#{Rails.application.config.client_name}" %> is an on-boarding bot for the RubyND Slack team.</h3><br>


<div class="ui four column grid">
  <div class="column center aligned messages" >
    <h2 class="ui center aligned icon header">
    <a href="/messages" title="">
      <i class="circular send icon" id="yellow" data-content="<%="#{Rails.application.config.client_name.capitalize}" %> sends messages to new Slack users at specified intervals. For example, a message can be sent welcoming a student while another is scheduled to follow up 5 days later." data-variation="very wide" data-position="bottom center"></i>
    </a>
  Messages
</h2>
    Schedule messages to send to students

  </div>

  <div class="column center aligned">
   <h2 class="ui center aligned icon header">
   <a href="/blasts" title="">
    <i class="circular announcement icon" id="red" data-content="Blasts will send a direct message from <%="#{Rails.application.config.client_name}" %> to every member of your slack team." data-position="bottom center"></i>
   </a>
  Blasts
</h2>
  Send a DM from <%="#{Rails.application.config.client_name}" %> to all users.
  </div>

  <div class="column center aligned">
   <h2 class="ui center aligned icon header">
   <a href="/interactions" title="">
    <i class="circular comments icon" id="teal" data-content="Users can also interact with <%="#{Rails.application.config.client_name}" %>. The bot will respond to specified user input with a corresponding response." data-position="bottom center"></i>
  </a>
  Interactions
</h2>
Create specific responses to user commands
  </div>
  <div class="column center aligned">
    <h2 class="ui center aligned icon header">
    <a href="/users" title="">
      <i class="circular users icon" id="blue" data-content="A list of information about current Slack team members." data-position="bottom center"></i>
    </a>
  Users
</h2>
View and search the list of slack users

  </div>
</div>

<div class="ui divider"> </div>

  <p>This is a brand new project, and feedback is warmly welcomed. Please ping @fuzz or @colt. You can also reach us via email at steven.worley@udacity.com and colt@udacity.com with suggestions, problems, advice, etc.</p>

  </div>
</div>
